info.name: Cambro Sofa
info.description: There’s more to the Cambro Sofa than meets the eye. Part of the Blu Dot x Fab collaboration, the living room lounger is simple, sophisticated, and yes—super cush under your tush. But this dark gray beauty sits on a secret. It comes with eight interchangeable legs—four steel and four wood—so you can customize the overall look and feel to suit your fancy.
